程序包 cn.ficos.Compiler.Syntax

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    MangoListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by MangoParser.
    MangoVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by MangoParser.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    MangoBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of MangoListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    MangoBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of MangoVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
